text:
[Verse]
Moonlight on the pavement
Stars in the sky
Feet on the ground
It's you and I

[Verse 2]
Whispers in the breeze
Shadows on the walls
Walking down the street
As the night falls

[Chorus]
Midnight stroll
Heart and soul
Hold me close
Never let go

[Verse 3]
Laughter in the dark
Night is ours to keep
Moments like these
Feel like a dream

[Verse 4]
City lights are twinkling
Silent serenade
With every step we take
Memories we made

[Chorus]
Midnight stroll
Heart and soul
Hold me close
Never let go
title: Midnight Stroll
